						</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		
		</div>
	<hr>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-3">
				<h4 Style="margin-top: 10px; "> 참여중인 채팅 </h4>
				<div class="user_list">

				</div>
			
			</div>
			<div class="col-9 chatpart" >
			
				<h3 style="text-align:center; margin-top: 60px; color: gray;"> 선택된 채팅방이 없습니다.</h3>
				<div id="chatPlace">
					<div class="row">
					
						<div class="col-8">
							<div id="selectUser" >	</div>
						</div>
